

1 D am hahawa ha cheha g Pilate g shondal mat wo s‑koꞌokam gewitta g Jesus. Kud wa woho hab e juh 2 k am hahawa ge hoꞌi gihkot k ab wahki moꞌoj ab k ab wahki g kownal kahba 3 k wabsh has ahg ch hab kaij, “Wapt wo si tash d Tutuligo ha‑kownaligk,” ch ab hahawa si shonikkash. 

4 D am ep i wuhsh g Pilate k hab kaij am ha wui g hemajkam, “Nehꞌe, ab ant ep wo i wuhshad k wo em‑chehgi mant pi haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh g pi ap chuꞌijig mas hekaj wo e muhkid.” 5 Md am hahawa i wuhshad k ab wabsh kia wahkch g hoꞌi gihko ch hegai kownal kahba. 

D hab kaij g Pilate ab ha wui, “Ab g wo i neid mo d wabsh si shoꞌig oꞌodham.” 

6 D am i nei g uꞌugchu papal ch cheopi nuhkuddam k si s‑kaidam hab wabsh ge kaij muꞌikko, “Muꞌani\! Muꞌani ab kots t ab\!” 

D g Pilate hab kaij, “Pegih, k wo be k ahpim ab wo mua kots t ab. Ahni ant hi pi haꞌichu shaꞌi cheh mas melchkwua g kownal chehanig mat wo e muhkid.” 

7 D hab kaij hegam Tutuligo, “Ahchim at hi melchkwua g t‑chehanig am hugkam mat hemho wa wo e muhkid no pi hab e aꞌaga mo d Jiosh alidag.” 

8 Neh, d am i ha kah g Pilate mad hab kaij idam k baꞌich i e ebkiod 9 k gam hu uhpam i wah k hab kaij ab Jesus wui, “Bahp amjed him?” 

D wabshaba g Jesus pi ab hu has shaꞌi chei. 

10 D hab ep kaij g Pilate ab wui, “Aha, napt pi has wo chei ab ni‑wui k eda s‑mahch mani gewkdag mant wo m‑dagito o ab wo m‑mua kots t ab\!” 

11 D hab kaij g Jesus ab wui, “Jiosh at ab m‑mah hegai gewkdag. K heg hekaj si pi ap hab e wua idam Caiaphas mo m‑piꞌichud mapt pi ap wo hekaj g e‑gewkdag.” 

12 D am i kah g Pilate ihda k am ep i wuhsh ha wui k am chum si e nako mat wo dagito. D wabshaba si s‑babgam hihnk hegam hahaꞌichu ch hab kaij, “Nehꞌe, ihda hemajkam o hab e ahg mo d si geꞌe kownal ch heg hekaj ab wui kehk hegai mo d si geꞌe kownal ch ab Rome t ab. Kupki ahpi hab waꞌap ab wui kehk g si geꞌe kownal mapt wo sha dagito ihda.” 

13 D am i kah g Pilate ihda k am hahawa i wuhshad g Jesus k heg ga hu i dahiwua usagakam daikud ed amai mach hab aꞌaga Gabbatha mo an sha uhgk i hodaitas. 

14 D eda e aihim g dahm juhk. Kud wo e kokda g kahwal mahmad imhab i juhk mat wo e wuhshad g t‑shohshon ha‑doꞌibiadag. D hab kaij g Pilate ab ha wui g hahaꞌichu, “Ia g hu wo neid g e‑kownalig.” 

15 D ab ep si s‑babgam hihnk ch hab kaij, “Muꞌani\! Muꞌani ab kots t ab\!” 

D hab kaij g Pilate, “Aha nam tatchua mant wo mua g si uhgk em‑kownalig ab kots t ab?” 

D hab kaij g uꞌugchu papal, “Heg o d waꞌi si uhgk t‑kownalig mo ab daha Rome t ab.” 

16 D am hahawa i dagito g Pilate g Jesus mamt ab wo mua kots t ab. 

**Mamtsh ab naggia g Jesus kots t ab **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:32-44; Mark 15:21-32; Luke 23:26-43 *

D am hab hahawa e juh g ha‑tatchui mamt ab ha mah g Jesus. D gam hu i wanim. 17 D g Jesus am kushwiot g hejel e‑kots. Kuchd am dada amai mo am e kokda. Bach aꞌaga amai Golgotha mo hab d ahga Koshwak. 18 Kumt gam si wuahawua g wehschugaj k ab sisish kots t ab k ab uhgk i bei. D eda gohk d ep lilso. Kumd idam hab waꞌap ab ha sisish kokots t ab k gan hu aꞌaijed ha chuhcha Jesus hugid an. 

19 D an sisishp g tapial Jesus kots t ab. K an ab hab chuꞌig: 

“Id o d Jesus ch d ha‑kownalig g Tutuligo.” 

20 K eda pi mehk ab kihhim t amjed amai mam am ha kokda. D heg hekaj muꞌijj g t‑wehm oꞌodham ab neꞌokchul hegai mo haschu an oꞌohanas. K an oꞌohanas g t‑neꞌokikaj ch g Rome neꞌokikaj ch g Greek neꞌokikaj. 

21 D gam hu uhpam ep hihi g uꞌugchu papal Pilate wui am i neꞌokchulidk ihda k hab ahg, “Pi g hab masma an oꞌohan mo d t‑kownalig k wabshaba an oꞌohan mo heg hejel hab kaij mo d t‑kownalig.” 

22 D hab kaij g Pilate ab ha wui, “Mant haschu an i oꞌoha, t heg an wo oꞌohadagk.” 

23 D hegam shondal mad am naggia g Jesus d giꞌik ch hekaj am giꞌikpa e tahpad g Jesus wepschuga. K am hema d si s‑namkig haꞌichu eniga ch pi hebai ha shohmas. 24 D id hab ahg g shondal ch hab kaij ab aꞌai e wui, “Pi att am hu aꞌai wo t‑wanchid ihda k am wabsh wo t‑chichwi matt hedai wo t‑gehg k heg wo bei.” Neh, bad kaij ch woho am hab e juh. Kud hab masma am e wohokamch g Jiosh oꞌohana mo an oꞌohanas hab masma: 

T am aꞌai wo e tahpani g wehschugaj g Jiosh si Kehsha k am wabsh wo e chichwi k wo s‑mai mat hedai wo bei g s‑namkig haꞌichu enigaj. *Isaiah 22:18 * 

25 D am gegok g jeꞌej ch jiskaj g Jesus miabidch amai mo am naggia. Kud gohk am ep ha wehmaj mo hema d hegai Mary mo g wehmaj kihkam d Clopas ch hema d ep Mary Magdalene. 26 Nid ahni am ha wehm kehk mo ni‑hekaj si pihk e elid g Jesus. Kud g Jesus an ni‑aꞌaga ch hab ahg g e‑jeꞌe, “Neh, id at d haha wo m‑madk m in kehk,” 27 ch hab ep ni‑ahg, “Id at d haha wo m‑jeꞌek.” Neh, nid am i amjed bei g jeꞌej. Kud heg am t‑wehm kih. 

**Matsh muh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:45-56; Mark 15:33-41; Luke 23:44-49 *

28 D hahawa s‑mahch g Jesus mat wehs hab juh mat haschu hab wo chum juh mat koi wo muh ch hab kaij, “Tonom ant.” 29 D an hema daha g haꞌa mad am shuhdagi g pad nawait. D am hema g shondal haꞌichu wakch pad nawait ch ed k an haꞌichu k an uskon k ab uhgk i be k ab kams hab masma mo an oꞌohadag Jiosh heki hu oꞌohana ed. 30 D ab i winiun k hab hahawa kaij, “Ia ant i wehs haꞌichu nahto.” Neh, bad kaij ch am hahawa jumal i moꞌowua k am i muh. 

**Mamtsh ab si chuꞌakad g Jesus hudaj ab **

31 D am e nakog g hemajkam mat wo e mihshmad nat pi g baꞌich tash d wo shahwaik ch d wo geꞌe tashk. Kutsh g hahaꞌichu ab kakke g Pilate mat wo e ohmi g ha‑kakhio hegam mad am nahngia. T hab wo e oiwigi g ha‑muhkig mat gam hu wo i e uꞌu k pi ab wabsh wo kia nahngiak t‑mihshmda tash ed, wahm mat id d wo si geꞌe t‑tashgak. 32 D ab ha chehani g Pilate g shondal mat wo ha ohmi g ha‑kakhio. Kud hab ha juh hegam gohk mo ab hugidaj ab nahngia g Jesus. 33 D wabshaba g Jesus heki hu muh. Kud pi ohmi g kakhioj. 34 D hema g shondal g e‑is‑pahyokaj chuꞌakad g Jesus ab hudaj ab. Kud ab ha hekaj si e iawua g ehꞌed ch shuhdagi. 35 Id anid neid ch s‑mahch mat woho muh. Kuni hab masma am em‑ahgidahim mamt ahpim hab waꞌap wo s‑mahch mat woho muh. 36 Jiosh oꞌohana o hab chuꞌig: 

Pi at hema wo shaꞌi e mul g ohꞌoj. *Exodus 12:46; Psalm 34:20 * 

Kut wa woho hab masma hab e juh. 

37 K an ep oꞌohanas ch hab chuꞌig: 

Hemajkam at ab wo neidad hegai mamt ab chuꞌakad. *Zechariah 12:10 * 

**Mamtsh ged hu cheh g Jesus **

*An g neid g Matthew 27:57-61; Mark 15:42-47; Luke 23:50-56 *

38 K hema d Joseph ch ab Arimathea t amjed ch s‑wohochud mo g Jesus d Jiosh si Kehsha ch wabshaba s‑ha gihug hegam mo pi hohhoꞌid. D wabshaba hekid am i muh g Jesus, d id am hih Pilate wui k ab e shoꞌigchud k ab tahni g honshpadaj. D am i hiwigi. D ga hu ep jiwia k ab i huduni g muhki k gam hu i bei. 39 D heg am ep haꞌichug Nicodemus mat wa ged hu i wehpeg chehgim g Jesus chuhug ch ed. Idam atsh s‑ap wo juh g muhki. D g Nicodemus heg hekaj uꞌa g siant s‑wehch hegai mo d s‑ap uhw haꞌichu ch d myrrh ch aloes. 

40-42 S‑e ad hohtkid nad pi hudunihim. D baꞌich tash d t‑mihshmda tash. K eda an mia cheotas hodai ch ed mamt am hab juh g hihaꞌini k wabshaba koi shaꞌi hekaj. K an wehgaj eshas g uꞌus. Kumd am i bei g honshpadag k am i hobino g s‑kehg ikuskaj heg wehnadk s‑ap uhw haꞌichu mach hab masma hab ha wua g koꞌi k am cheh heg eda hihaꞌini k gam hu hihi. 

